232
00:20:47.818 --> 00:20:49.819
We're talking about
a disbarred alcoholic

233
00:20:49.874 --> 00:20:52.125
who represented Leanne
in her first trial.

234
00:20:52.220 --> 00:20:54.680
and a star witness who was
a known drug trafficker

235
00:20:54.736 --> 00:20:55.891
with a sweetheart deal.

236
00:20:55.954 --> 00:20:59.086
All that. I'd say.
adds up to some doubt.

237
00:21:00.470 --> 00:21:03.681
That was enough for a retrial.
a do-over.

238
00:21:03.812 --> 00:21:05.498
This...

239
00:21:05.663 --> 00:21:08.241
